<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.christendom-awake.org/pages/ratzinger/liberationtheol.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.christendom-awake.org/pages/ratzinger/liberationtheol.htm" rel="nofollow">"Liberation Theology"</a> by Cardinal Ratzinger at Christendom Awake</li>
